

Things that should be done to the 3.0 release:


	1. remove all kow_config dependency in modules in favour of a kow_lib.json.object_type
		Status.URI_Parameters	=> Status.Request_Parameters/Attributes (figure out a cooler name)
	2. implement a method for retrieving specific configurations
		Get_Config( Component, Config := "setup" ); => ./components/[component]/[config].cfg
		Get_Config( Service, Config := "setup" );   => ./components/[component]/[service]_service/[config].cfg
		Get_Config( Module, Config := "setup" );    => ./components/[component]/[module]_module/[config].cfg



The config (and resource) path should be default to:
	./
	./data/
